description: The truth behind Fitz's turn could bring down all of S.H.I.E.L.D.
name: No Regrets

description: In need of some real R&R, the team gears up to leave for a company retreat when supervillain Dr. Psycho releases a toxic gas in Charm City. Now stuck in the Wayne Security offices, Emily (Vanessa Hudgens) does her best to make the most of a terrible situation.
name: Emergency Punch-Up

description: When Fred (Luke Perry) decides to finalize the divorce with Archie's mother Mary (guest-star Molly Ringwald), Archie (KJ Apa) hides his true feelings. Archie tries to win Valerie (guest-star Hayley Law) back with a romantic evening, however, Betty (Lili Reinhart) hijacks his plans when she decides to throw Jughead (Cole Sprouse) a surprise birthday party. Once Cheryl (Madelaine Petsch) learns of the party, she decides to make it interesting and things quickly get out of control. Meanwhile, Veronica (Camila Mendes) contemplates whether she should participate in the deposition to help get her Dad released.
name: The Lost Weekend
The Resurrection of Cell and Frieza

deck: Atfer witnessing the first battle between Ultraman and Gudis, UMA Mars explorer Jack Shindo mysteriously returns to Earth with Ultraman's powers when Earth becomes Gudis' next target as it disperses a virus that effects the planet's environment and turning lifeforms into gigantic, mutated monsters.
description: UMA Mars explorers Jack Shino and Stanley Haggard witness a colossus battle Ultraman and Gudis. Stunning Ultraman, Gudis destroys the space capsule as Stan tries to escape. Ultraman recovers to defeat Gudis but, before the creature is destroyed it escapes to Earth as a luminescent green virus. The effects of the virus are felt on Earth as infected life forms are mutated into gigantic monsters. Jack Shindo mysteriously appears on Earth.
name: Signs of Life

deck: As the polar icecaps are being melted by Gudis Cells, it awakens a Gigasaurus, a dinosaur that is capable of producing abilities. Meanwhile, UMA recruits Jack Shindo to be an agent after he mysteriously returns and has insight knowledge about Gudis Cells unaware he is Ultraman.
name: The Hibernator

deck: When a young Jimmy Martin uncovers a Gerukadon fossil, his becomes possessed by Gudis Cells as his dreams make the Gerukadon come to life and attack the city.
name: A Child's Dream

deck: UMA agents Jack Shindo and Lloyd Wilder are sent to investigate a whirlwind that attacked two hunters. Could it be an Aboriginal god striking against humanity for their crimes against nature, or is it driven by the Gudis?
name: The Storm Hunter

deck: Stanley Haggard has returned from Mars. But is it the real Stan or Gudis himself?
name: Blast From The Past

deck: U.M.A. is in absolute crisis: one of their team members is infected by Gudis Cells, an aggressive and reckless army general seizes control of U.M.A., and Gudis is about to evolve into its final form. Can Jack Shindo and Ultraman save the Earth from Gudis once and for all?
name: The Showdown

deck: A little girl is lost when she flees from a giant guardian, who is trying to protect the forest from land developers. Its a race against time as U.M.A. is sent for a search & rescue mission and tackle the guardian as well.
name: The Forest Guardian

deck: Pests and toxins are in the air in a big way, and it might have to do with a shady farmer. What secret is the farmer trying to hide from U.M.A.?
name: Bitter Harvest

deck: A university professor's plan for a bio-technical revolution might be sprouting a hidden agenda as people are disappearing and the plants are grown out of control. Where is the root of the problem coming from?
name: The Biospherians

deck: Earth is about to play host to some unexpected visitors. A mysterious woman takes an interest in U.M.A. agent Charles Morgan while her food truck acts even stranger, aggressive, and perhaps jealous.
name: Tourists From The Stars

deck: A U.F.O. hidden away in a military hanger is emitting a strange power and a mad man is obese with its secrets.
name: The Survivalists

deck: A relic from the past surfaces with a prophecy that can end the world as a monster from the air and another from the sea attack the Earth. Their combined strength might be too much for Ultraman to handle.
name: The Age of Plagues

deck: The end is nigh. The Earth's fate rests with U.M.A. as they try to solve the relic's divination riddle and Ultraman's last stand against two opponents.
name: Nemesis
Stuck in the Middle Ages with You

deck: An evil plastic surgeon is turning beautiful models into ugly, obese women.
name: Beauty and the Obese Part 1
It's How You Play the Game
Boy Bands Will Be Boy Bands
